  lines:
  - speakerName: "V\u0169"
    englishSpeakerName: Vu
    text: "\u01A0... chi\u1EBFc v\u00F2ng \u0111\u00E3 m\u1EA5t c\u1EE7a Silly \u0111\u00E2y m\u00E0."
    englishText: Huh... this is Silly's lost collar.
    portrait: {fileID: -4254258901546231152, guid: c5d997eca51e38d418373f1e8fdc90ce, type: 3}
  - speakerName: "V\u0169"
    englishSpeakerName: Vu
    text: "M\u00ECnh c\u1EA7n mang n\u00F3 l\u00EAn ph\u00F2ng ng\u1EE7 \u0111\u1EC3 c\u1EA5t l\u1EA1i."
    englishText: I should take it upstairs to the bedroom and put it away.
    portrait: {fileID: -4254258901546231152, guid: c5d997eca51e38d418373f1e8fdc90ce, type: 3}
